{"tid":1698204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好成日屌新加坡人坡狗住，不如試下connect埋佢哋？","createTime":"2019-11-07T10:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:04:50.000Z","uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7eab865ede3b3790e745d3ef39304d0a26d7671","tid":1698204,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"頭先睇下面依個post 見到有好多巴絲入去新加坡警察個fb扮支那人曲線留言 激到班坡仔同馬拉仔(唔知點解咩都關佢地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)扎扎跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忽然諗到 點解唔襯華記依個絕佳機會connect埋佢地呢?大家一齊諗下點玩先可以令班新加坡同馬拉人愈黎愈憎支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfq9xqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnfq9xqM.jpg&h=e0f81636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/singaporepoliceforce/posts/10159066438329408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsingaporepoliceforce%2Fposts%2F10159066438329408&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=fe2bfbd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/singaporepoliceforce/posts/10159066438329408</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡警察證實扣起華記呀叔本passport，並調查一宗違反Public Order Act罪行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698081</a>"},{"pid":"4f2b58386d404be520d2098a4b46900bd1b693d2","tid":1698204,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25d83f6a84bb33f63b4e45554245ce140bb543e","tid":1698204,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"(認真非玩野）華記呢個蝴蝶效應分分鐘真係可以connect埋新加坡人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693599</a>"},{"pid":"e844